messages.message: Amazing how teema calls out to not being micro managing and this is exactly the problem I am struggling with. Coincidence? I think not. Can I have a job?

Sorry for the delay, Brian. Teema is a staffing agency, we have clients that I may be able to get you an interview with....

Not sure if I have anything right now? What are your strongest skills in terms of programming?
C# PHP JavaScript user experience. I meant a job with teema not from teema.
Haha I know what you meant, we aren't hiring for anything related to IT/development at the moment :(
I think my collar is already turning blue.
